notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-10T11:18:14.546Z",maintainer-agent,"Verification evidence (2026-07-10): root cause was discoverPmRootFromAncestors probing only <dir>/.agents/pm/settings.json. Fix adds root-layout adoption of <dir>/settings.json guarded by pm markers (id_prefix or item_format) with .agents/pm precedence per level; explicit --path/PM_PATH unchanged. Live sandbox: bare pm create/stats now resolve a pm init <dir> workspace; integration probe extension receives pm_root == workspace root and the documented spawn-back (pm --pm-path <ctx.pm_root> stats) exits 0. Full fast suite 270 files / 5510 tests green. Also confirmed the defect was broader than GH-495 reported: plain pm create failed from the workspace before the fix, so GH-488's --pm-path-scoped follow-ups were masking discovery blindness."
